This artifact is a parameter-efficient LoRA fine-tuning adapter (trained with QLoRA, 4-bit NF4
quantisation, NEFTune) over the base model Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct, which is licensed under
Apache-2.0 (© Alibaba Cloud / Qwen Team).

Significant change (Apache-2.0 §4): additive low-rank adapter weights only. Trained with a fixed
random seed 11 on the CodeFeedback-KG Spanish code-feedback dataset, on a single NVIDIA RTX 5090.
The base model is not redistributed here; only the adapter weights, tokenizer and chat template.
